    "This fusion method ensures that GPT always refers to the contextual representation of BERT in the process of generating text, thereby improving the coherence and accuracy of the generated text.During the model training process, we use maximum likelihood estimation (MLE) as the loss function to minimize the difference between the generated text and the target text.",
